Package: ShinyPDBPainter
Title: Proteomics painter of 3D Molecular Structures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nikeisha",
           family = "Caruana",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "nikeisha.caruana@unimelb.edu.au")
Description: Provides an 'htmlwidgets' <https://www.htmlwidgets.org/> interface to 'NGL.js' <http://nglviewer.org/ngl/api/>, specially built from ShinyNGLVieweR from nvelden <https://github.com/nvelden/shinyNGLVieweR/tree/master/R>.
    'ShinyPDBPainter' can be used to visualize and interact with protein databank ('PDB') and structural files in R and Shiny applications, specially to paint protein complexes using proteomics data. 
    It includes a set of API functions to manipulate the viewer after creation in Shiny.
